OL,5, The son of murdered soldier Lee Rigby  
OL,6, has raised more than #40,000 to help   
OL,7, other bereaved forces children and "in 
OL,8, honour" of his father.                 
OL,10,FJack Rigby, 12, was two years old when 
OL,11,Fhis father was murdered by Islamist    
OL,12,Fextremists outside Woolwich Barracks.  
OL,14,FJack, who now lives in Halifax, West   
OL,15,FYorkshire, is raising money for the    
OL,16,FScotty's Little Soldiers charity.      
OL,18,FHe has run a total of 26.2 miles this  
OL,19,Fmonth to mark the 10th anniversary of  
OL,20,Fhis father's death on 22 May 2013.     
